``polars arg-sort``
[link: /commands/categories/dataframe.md] ’Щ@ff5c1d17040925c6f29b7583e5f1c5b827b7c8c5372503af0e8989d84226ccadЩVTitle: title: polars arg-sort
Path: Signature
Content:
``> polars arg-sort {flags} ``
’Щ@489756867336f051d1ca852b44307ca937720019966dde101b9b8a1d13202842Ъ!Title: title: polars arg-sort
Path: Flags
Content:
``--reverse, -r``
: Reverse order.
``--nulls-last, -n``
: Nulls ordered last.
``--limit, -l {int}``
: Limit a sort output, this is for optimization purposes and might be ignored.
``--maintain-order, -m``
: Maintain order on sorted items.
